Time-Frequency Analysis ...

Gabor Transform

  • Fourier Transform: $$ F(\omega) = \int_{-\infty}^{\infty} f(t) e^{i\omega t}dt$$

  • STFT => Gabor : $$ G_g[f](t,\omega) = \widetilde{f}_g (t,\omega) = \int_{-\infty}^{\infty} f(\tau)g(\tau-t) e^{i\omega \tau}d\tau$$

Window Fourier Transform is just like ... Music Sheets ...

It include the frequency information (chord) ) at each time slice (bar) ...

  • http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LL_WI12QH_0
  • http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chord_(music)
  • http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bar_(music)

print "~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~"
print "/ ".join(vcr.tokenize_gen(lambda text:vcr.jieba.cut(vcr.nltk.clean_html(text)))(u"<p></p>"))
print "~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~"

jieba_without_html_tokenizer = vcr.tokenize_gen(lambda text:vcr.jieba.cut(vcr.nltk.clean_html(text)))
unigram_without_html_tokenizer = vcr.tokenize_gen(lambda text:tkr.ngram(vcr.nltk.clean_html(text),n=1))
bigram_without_html_tokenizer = vcr.tokenize_gen(lambda text:tkr.ngram(vcr.nltk.clean_html(text),n=2))

print "/ ".join(jieba_without_html_tokenizer(u"<p></p>"))
print "/ ".join(unigram_without_html_tokenizer(u"<p></p>"))
print "/ ".join(bigram_without_html_tokenizer(u"<p></p>"))

Solving of Optimization Problems:

Linear Programming:

$$ \begin{eqnarray} \min_{x_1,x_2} x_1 & + & x_2 \\ 2x_1 & + & x_2 & \geq 1 \\ x_1 & + & 3x_2 & \geq 1 \\ x_1 &&& \geq 0 \\ x_2 &&& \geq 0 \\ \end{eqnarray}$$

Min-Max Problem:

$$ \begin{eqnarray} \min_{x_1,x_2} \max( x_1 & , & x_2 ) \\ 2x_1 & + & x_2 & \geq 1 \\ x_1 & + & 3x_2 & \geq 1 \\ x_1 &&& \geq 0 \\ x_2 &&& \geq 0 \\ \end{eqnarray}$$

Quadratic Programming:

$$ \begin{eqnarray} \min_{x_1,x_2} x_1^2 & + & 9x_2^2 \\ 2x_1 & + & x_2 & \geq 1 \\ x_1 & + & 3x_2 & \geq 1 \\ x_1 &&& \geq 0 \\ x_2 &&& \geq 0 \\ \end{eqnarray}$$
